metadata.name: Maxie #1
metadata.description: A community-driven collectibles project featuring art by Maxity. Maxie come in a joyful range of colors, traits and sizes representing elements on Earth with a collection size of 1,000. Each Maxie allows its owner to enter the Maxity Symbiotic Metaverse and enjoy the exclusive benefits of Maxity ecosystem. Maxie NFT can also be used as an Avatar in the Maxity DApp.
